&lt;strong&gt;What is PT Caleb Technology?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
PT Caleb Technology is a company that focusing in System integrator to integrated Instrument System and PCS/ Process Control System, SIS Safety Instrumented System, SCADA System, Metering Package and Power Generation.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;What is the main business of PT Caleb Technology?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Our main business are Control System &amp;amp; Instrumentation, Fire and Gas Alarm System, Gas Metering Package, and Power Generation.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;What is PT Caleb Technology capabalities?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Our capabilities are developing an integrated system for FGS (Fire and Gas System), PCS (Process Control System), SIS (Safety Instrumented System), SCADA System, Metering Package and Power Generation.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;How to make partnership with PT Caleb Technology?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
You can contact us on the Contact Us Page to make partnership with us.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Who Should I contact to business?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
If you are interested in establishing business with us on the Contact Us page there is also the contact person for each Department Manager who can be contacted directly that might be relevant on your business scope.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;What is PT Caleb Technology Product?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
We offer products confirming to System Integration, thus facilitating our clients to globalize their applications for Oil and Gas industrial, Power Plant &amp;amp; Automation including design, installation and services after sales.
